articles.description: The short-handed San Francisco 49ers saw their season end Saturday night, with a 41-6 loss to the Seattle Seahawks, but running back Christian McCaffrey and his teammates spoke after the defeat about the pride they have in overcoming the odds this year.
articles.headline: Proud San Francisco 49ers quickly turn page to next season
